CatDescriptText: The inscription on the postcard reads, "Modu Square With Merry Christmas Modu Wish You A Happy And Prosperous New Year Mr. & Mrs. T. V. Cole 56 Gurley St Monrovia Dec 1964." The postcard also has pictures of a bedroom and living room.
TitMainTitle: Copy of photograph of postcard with man wearing Kente cloth toga, women with large earrings and building with inscription, "Modu Square With Merry Christmas Modu Wish You A Happy And Prosperous New Year"
